item.title: Vesta's Spear *NOT NEW, NOT MINE*
item.dc:creator: @reyx7 reyx7
item.description:
@reyx7 wrote:

[quote=“the wanderer, post:10, topic:372553”][quote author=Mod-Vlad- link=topic=468599.msg3426633#msg3426633 date=1291992315]

To @reyx7: I “probably” don’t care about a reputation I’m on MoparScape to get help and try help others with stuff I can do!

To @Cole1497: I uploaded this because like 30 people asked me to do it. They also was asking for all other Pvp Armours, but I had no time to upload it.

To @h1 sk1ller: Don’t want this <sh*t>? Why post here then? -.-

“with stuff I can do!” Or with stuff JaGeX can do for you.
“because like 30 people asked me to do it.” Are they too lazy to use the search? Read the rules of the section.
“Why post here then? -.-” He mean’t “we” as a community.

“with stuff I can do!” Or with stuff JaGeX can do for you. (
I mean in stuff I can do - searching faster, coding other stuff, that is what I mean.

Dude , relax… I’ve just have made this post because I’ve had in-need to do it.
and yeah, maybe those 30 people are lazy to use search.

Relax , just let it be.
[/quote]
I’ll let it be if you can show me some intelligence. Right now you in my eyes you look like someone who knows nothing about animation, or even say modeling, and you leeched someone else work of putting a Vesta’s spear into a client, hoping that people would say THANKS I WANTED THIS. Well those people who are too lazy to use the search button don’t deserve this.[/quote]
This. I’d prefer if stuff like this was posted in client hacking. This section is for models NOT MADE BY JAGEX. We’ve been lucky to have not seen a skillcape in weeks. But unless you have a homemade model, please don’t post here. I wanna see if I can get a mod like CJ to approve this.
